<br>
  Goto www.pricewatch.com to get prices. Then check the reputation of the seller at www.resellerratings.com and go from there.<br>
<br>
  At the moment an AMD 2 gig chip is about $86 3 year warranty box from Googlegear. A geforce 4 about $154 at Newegg.com 512 meg of Ram varies but I just paid $127 for a stick over the weekend, but memory prices are volitile and jump up and down a lot.<br>
<br>
  I would guess about $475-$500 US will but you a new CPU Memory Video Card and System board.<br>
<br>
  Also it pays to spend a few extra dollars to buy from a reputable dealer instead of the lowest price you can find, why I suggested Resellerratings.com.<br>
<br>
  The 2 companies I have recently dealt with that did a great job was Newegg ( www.newegg.com ) and Essential Computers of New York at ( www.essencompu.com ) both shipped fast, and well packaged. <br>
<br>
  Good luck on your new computer.<br>
<br>
Calebe<br>
